course_title: Theory and Practice in Human Geography

WL1.comments: Note: This is a wait list for GEOG 345, lecture section 101, Term 1. You will be moved into active registration if space becomes available. Wait list does not guarantee placement in this course.

description: A consideration of major intellectual issues and debates in the development of contemporary human geography, in relation to developments in other fields and changes in politics, culture and society.
